<h2>What Makes an Effective HVAC Van Wrap?</h2>

<p class="body-text">The best HVAC van wraps follow a proven formula for maximum lead generation:</p>

<ul class="services">
<li><em>Large Phone Number</em> — Readable from 50+ feet away. This is the #1 call-to-action that drives business from van wraps.</li>
<li><em>Clear Service List</em> — "Heating · Cooling · Installation · Repair" tells potential customers exactly what you do at a glance.</li>
<li><em>24/7 Emergency Callout</em> — If you offer emergency service, make it prominent. This drives the highest-value calls.</li>
<li><em>License Number</em> — Illinois law requires displaying your contractor license. A wrapped van with a visible license number builds trust.</li>
